# random duel scenario selection example

# There are a total of 15 possible duels. The ones listed first
# are known to be most problematic and thus are disabled by default.

# of course, this config file goes best with
MaxTeams 2

#RBegin
#Territory1 Russia
#Territory2 Asia
#REnd

#RBegin
#Territory1 Europe
#Territory2 Africa
#REnd

# the following two are also slighly in favour against South America,
# you may want to disable them as well.

RBegin
Territory1 SouthAmerica
Territory2 Europe
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 SouthAmerica
Territory2 Africa
REnd

# the rest is generally allright.

RBegin
Territory1 NorthAmerica
Territory2 SouthAmerica
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 NorthAmerica
Territory2 Europe
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 NorthAmerica
Territory2 Russia
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 NorthAmerica
Territory2 Asia
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 NorthAmerica
Territory2 Africa
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 SouthAmerica
Territory2 Russia
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 SouthAmerica
Territory2 Asia
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 Europe
Territory2 Russia
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 Europe
Territory2 Asia
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 Russia
Territory2 Africa
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 Asia
Territory2 Africa
REnd

